  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink293-kilavi">pakaṟkuṟiyiṭam pukka talaimakaṉ talaivi piṉṉāka maṟaiya vantu kaṇputaittuḻic colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the hero, who entered the daytime tryst, said, when the heroine came stealthily behind [him] and covered [his] eyes.
                     
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink293">
<l>cilampukamaḻ kānta ṇaṟuṅkulai yaṉṉa</l>
<l>nalampeṟu kaiyiṉeṉ kaṇputait tōyē</l>
<l>pāya liṉṟuṇai yākiya paṇaittōṭ</l>
<l>ṭōkai māṭciya maṭantai</l>
<l>nīyala tuḷarōveṉ ṉeñcamarn tōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O you who covered my eyes—</l>
        <l>whose hands gain beauty,</l>
        <l>which are like the fragrant clusters of Malabar glory lilies</l>
        <l>fragrant on the mountain slopes—</l>
        <l rend="space">O girl who has become my sweet companion in bed,</l>
        <l>of bamboo shoulders and magnificence of a peacock—</l>
        <l>besides you, are there any</l>
        <l>who have dwelt in my heart?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
